                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I apprehended the prisoner in Laystall-street, from a description I had from other people.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> Miss James at first said she believed I was the man but she should not like to swear to me; a man there said I was the man, and that Mr. Mitchell had seen me; when he came, he said I was not the man, but it was a man similar to me; I was standing in Leather-lane when I was taken, where I should not have been if guilty.</p>
               <p>
